WEBVTT

00:41.249 --> 00:44.668
CJ Entertainment
and Barunson Present

00:51.217 --> 00:54.762
A Barunson
Sio Film Production

00:59.225 --> 01:03.270
Executive Producer
Katharine KIM

01:05.523 --> 01:09.568
Associate Producer
Joon H. CHOI

01:12.238 --> 01:14.948
Investment Executives
Sean LEE, LEE Sang-moo

01:18.703 --> 01:21.413
Produced by
MOON Yang-kwon, Syd LIM

01:25.293 --> 01:26.460
Production Executive
SEO Woo-sik

01:26.503 --> 01:28.754
Why don't you take a seat?

01:30.590 --> 01:33.092
Co-Producer Danny PARK
Master told me
to be courteous.

01:35.303 --> 01:38.847
There's something
we need to sort out.

01:38.890 --> 01:39.681
Sort out?

01:40.141 --> 01:42.101
The issue of how you should
address the master.

01:43.311 --> 01:47.689
Don't worry.

01:48.149 --> 01:50.109
I may be of a higher class but

01:50.610 --> 01:52.986
I wouldn't use the plain
form with Mr. YI.

01:55.448 --> 01:59.201
But nonetheless
I want you to know

01:59.202 --> 02:03.872
my master's plainly spoken.

02:05.625 --> 02:06.667
I see.

02:12.215 --> 02:14.216
KIM Joo-hyuck,

02:14.217 --> 02:16.301
RYOO Seung-bum,
CHO Yeo-jeong

02:18.721 --> 02:23.892
Written and Directed
by KIM Dae-woo

02:32.318 --> 02:35.654
I made you come all this way
because I want this soup.

02:35.989 --> 02:38.949
- Sorry.
- Not at all.

02:41.077 --> 02:43.036
After you try it,

02:43.079 --> 02:44.288
you'll say
it's worth the trip.

02:44.330 --> 02:45.497
Yes, sir.

02:53.089 --> 02:56.508
I asked you to come

02:59.637 --> 03:05.267
because I'm not sure I'd make
a good subject for a novel

03:07.896 --> 03:09.479
What are you saying?

03:09.898 --> 03:12.399
I was so excited
I couldn't sleep last night

03:13.610 --> 03:16.486
You're the town's most
glamorous gangster...

03:19.991 --> 03:21.074
Me and my mouth.

03:21.534 --> 03:23.076
I'm sorry.
I shouldn't have said that

03:23.077 --> 03:24.578
You're right,
I am a gangster

03:27.332 --> 03:28.498
And

03:31.836 --> 03:34.087
you're at the top
ofthe beach reading heap

03:34.631 --> 03:35.714
Beach reading?

03:39.219 --> 03:40.969
I'm not sure if I'm the best

03:41.596 --> 03:45.849
Anyway,
thanks for choosing me

03:47.227 --> 03:49.061
Any writer

03:51.439 --> 03:54.316
would want to write
about you

04:02.242 --> 04:06.328
What did you do before?

04:07.830 --> 04:11.959
I used to be a servant.

04:13.878 --> 04:15.295
A servant!

04:17.340 --> 04:20.676
I went from here to there
until I was 30

04:22.178 --> 04:25.764
and I became
an aristocrat's servant.

04:27.433 --> 04:34.147
I shared a room
with a houseguest, Mr. MA.

04:41.197 --> 04:44.783
You're the new maid?

04:45.702 --> 04:48.287
Enjoying your life here?

04:49.706 --> 04:50.872
Yes, why do you ask?

04:52.500 --> 04:54.501
That's not the way.

04:55.086 --> 04:57.504
We should look each other
in the eye when we talk.

05:03.720 --> 05:08.598
People told me to be careful
when you're around.

05:10.351 --> 05:13.520
All gossip and rumors.

05:13.521 --> 05:14.313
It's hot!

05:15.440 --> 05:16.606
How silly!

05:17.900 --> 05:20.944
This is fun.
Can I come again?

05:21.696 --> 05:24.865
Sorry? Yes...

05:26.701 --> 05:28.160
Dear me!

05:36.210 --> 05:39.504
She was talking to me but
her eyes were on you.

05:41.090 --> 05:42.966
Sorry? Oh...

05:46.220 --> 05:47.679
It's hot!

05:49.640 --> 05:50.766
What are you doing?

05:53.811 --> 05:55.145
So hot!

06:04.197 --> 06:11.161
So, what's Mong like?

06:12.288 --> 06:14.498
It's only been a few days

06:14.999 --> 06:16.083
so I don't know.

06:17.710 --> 06:18.794
He's nice to me.

06:20.213 --> 06:21.171
Nice?

06:21.214 --> 06:24.966
He's given me clothes.

06:27.428 --> 06:28.678
Mong...

06:29.430 --> 06:32.391
I've known him
since he was a kid

06:34.268 --> 06:36.478
but still can't
figure him out.

06:43.820 --> 06:47.781
It wasn't a grand job
but I wanted to do my best.

06:49.283 --> 06:52.077
It must be tough
waiting around for me.

06:53.204 --> 06:54.788
Not at all, master.

06:58.084 --> 07:03.672
Then, I saw her.

07:22.817 --> 07:28.697
The scent offlowers
is all around

07:28.739 --> 07:34.661
From this peak to
that peak All around

07:39.709 --> 07:44.671
Butterflies
follow the scent

07:44.714 --> 07:48.800
Do you work here?

07:49.719 --> 07:50.677
Yeah,

07:52.221 --> 07:55.515
why do you ask?

07:56.392 --> 07:57.684
Who is she?

07:59.020 --> 08:03.690
She's the owner's daughter,

08:03.691 --> 08:05.233
Her name's Chun-hyang.

08:07.111 --> 08:08.236
I'm Hyang-dan.

08:08.279 --> 08:12.574
Butterfly,
drunk by the scent,

08:12.617 --> 08:18.163
don't sit on the petals

08:18.206 --> 08:29.257
For scented flowers
uphold their fidelity

08:34.388 --> 08:45.774
Don't come sit
on my petals

09:01.541 --> 09:03.083
Bang-ja!

09:06.212 --> 09:10.173
Go arrange a meeting.
Hurry!

09:33.823 --> 09:36.700
You can't follow me in here!

09:38.202 --> 09:44.958
My master wants a word
with you.

09:45.001 --> 09:46.459
Who's your master?

09:47.628 --> 09:49.671
He's the one that
got up earlier.

09:49.714 --> 09:52.465
The most handsome guy there.

09:52.800 --> 09:54.092
Handsome?

09:54.635 --> 09:56.803
Stop talking rubbish
and get out!

09:56.804 --> 09:58.471
You could just have a word
with him.

09:58.472 --> 09:59.806
I was wondering

10:00.808 --> 10:04.352
where you'd gone.
What are you doing here?

10:05.021 --> 10:06.980
I was telling her
about you, master.

10:17.199 --> 10:19.451
Such a grave indiscretion.

10:20.369 --> 10:23.455
I was a bit scared
but it's alright.

10:24.999 --> 10:26.374
You didn't have to hit him.

10:29.629 --> 10:32.088
I've been too kind to him.

10:36.218 --> 10:40.263
I'd like to invite you to tea
to apologize properly.

10:41.849 --> 10:45.393
What are you doing?

10:45.645 --> 10:51.358
Chun-hyang, I'm dying
waiting for you.

10:51.400 --> 10:53.068
I said no.

10:55.279 --> 10:57.781
But you sang
for the aristocrats.

10:58.491 --> 10:59.991
You have to play fair.

10:59.992 --> 11:00.992
Hey, you!

11:02.286 --> 11:06.456
I don't know what it's about

11:07.291 --> 11:08.792
but the lady said 'no.'

11:16.425 --> 11:19.469
Young master,
let me greet you.

11:20.012 --> 11:22.555
I'm Gwang of Tavern Street.

11:22.598 --> 11:24.683
Nice to meet you.

11:29.397 --> 11:32.440
Looks like you're
all fired up.

11:33.484 --> 11:36.194
But time to go home now.

11:36.195 --> 11:37.278
Don't do that...

11:37.321 --> 11:39.072
You can't order me around.

11:40.408 --> 11:42.784
You cant order me around

11:42.827 --> 11:49.791
You're enraging this lowly
nothing of a guy.

11:50.501 --> 11:52.085
Go home, now!

11:59.218 --> 12:00.343
Who the hell are you?

12:00.386 --> 12:03.638
I'm his servant.

12:03.723 --> 12:05.640
You servant!

12:07.727 --> 12:09.811
I'm alright, stand back.

12:28.038 --> 12:30.457
Where are you?

12:30.916 --> 12:31.958
Boss

12:50.019 --> 12:54.105
Chun-hyang...

12:55.691 --> 12:58.985
That was a big mistake.

13:00.237 --> 13:02.197
You shouldn't have done that.

13:03.657 --> 13:05.366
What was I supposed to do?

13:06.410 --> 13:10.455
You robbed Mong the chance

13:10.998 --> 13:12.540
to show off.

13:13.501 --> 13:16.002
And he hit you.

13:16.295 --> 13:17.879
Don't you have any pride?

13:20.216 --> 13:22.175
But I'm his servant.

13:28.682 --> 13:29.808
Was that the only reason?

13:31.936 --> 13:36.648
I guess.
This is making me angry.

13:39.902 --> 13:41.069
What shall I do?

13:41.111 --> 13:45.073
Of course, you'll have to
get her word on this.

13:45.908 --> 13:46.741
What?

13:47.827 --> 13:49.452
How can I do that?

13:51.205 --> 13:54.666
Let's deal
with Hyang-dan first.

13:55.334 --> 13:56.292
Sorry?

13:59.505 --> 14:02.090
I never teach
this to anyone. Never.

14:02.132 --> 14:03.758
Oh, please.

14:04.510 --> 14:07.762
You're in a tight spot
so I want to help.

14:08.430 --> 14:13.184
Tell her what needs
to be done.

14:13.185 --> 14:15.979
Walk back and forth
in front of her.

14:16.021 --> 14:18.648
That'll get her confused
and irritated.

14:18.691 --> 14:21.734
Don't take any notice
and focus on

14:21.777 --> 14:24.279
what you need to say
and then

14:24.321 --> 14:26.573
Then, just casually like this

14:30.953 --> 14:33.580
Grab hold of her right here.

14:40.421 --> 14:43.631
What? Grab her there?

14:43.674 --> 14:49.262
Not too fast, not too slow.
Like this.

14:54.602 --> 14:57.645
She's not going to
let me do that!

14:58.230 --> 14:59.272
She'll get away.

15:01.400 --> 15:02.567
Get away?

15:03.027 --> 15:04.485
Of course.

15:06.113 --> 15:10.992
Try again and see
if you can get away.

15:11.035 --> 15:14.495
You're walking
and she's talking.

15:14.538 --> 15:15.788
And grab!

15:17.917 --> 15:23.004
You can't get away.

15:27.009 --> 15:28.676
He's a weird servant.

15:29.511 --> 15:32.764
Other servants
don't get involved.

15:32.806 --> 15:34.265
Very brave!

15:35.225 --> 15:39.395
What if his master's
lost his nerve?

15:41.941 --> 15:45.485
He's caught the bait.

15:46.695 --> 15:49.697
He'll come back.
You'll see.

15:57.289 --> 16:02.001
A servant has come
from Lord YI's.

16:12.054 --> 16:16.849
Who told you to
make a decision?

16:17.309 --> 16:19.185
Just pass on the message.

16:21.814 --> 16:26.067
He wants to see her tomorrow

16:26.610 --> 16:28.486
by the waterfall.

16:29.405 --> 16:31.572
My mistress doesn't
go out with men.

16:31.615 --> 16:33.199
She's not like that.

16:33.200 --> 16:37.662
I don't care what she's like.
Just pass on the message.

16:37.705 --> 16:39.872
There's no point
in passing it on.

16:40.499 --> 16:42.583
You're so stubborn!

16:49.633 --> 16:53.886
What a lovely view.

16:56.515 --> 16:59.350
Why this sudden talk
ofthe view?

16:59.393 --> 17:00.351
Grab!

17:06.775 --> 17:13.114
Let's try to get along,
shall we?

17:19.121 --> 17:20.371
What did he say?

17:23.333 --> 17:26.294
His master wants to meet her

17:26.920 --> 17:27.879
And then?

17:29.548 --> 17:31.382
Answer me.

17:32.593 --> 17:34.385
So I said 'yes'.

17:34.970 --> 17:37.555
What?

17:39.141 --> 17:40.683
What was I supposed to do?

17:46.982 --> 17:49.484
What do nobles talk
about on a date?

17:51.612 --> 17:54.197
Maybe the same things we do.

17:57.326 --> 18:00.870
Aren't they hungry,
smelling this?

18:07.127 --> 18:08.753
They're not like us.

18:09.797 --> 18:12.381
They hide their feelings.

18:13.425 --> 18:17.762
Not shoving it down the throat
even if you're starving

18:19.306 --> 18:20.765
That's what being
an aristocrat is about.

18:21.433 --> 18:23.101
You're a bit
like one yourself.

18:27.231 --> 18:31.692
Stop talking
and focus on the meat.

18:35.739 --> 18:39.575
You're a good cook.

18:42.204 --> 18:44.747
What an odd thing
for a guy to be good at.

18:44.790 --> 18:47.959
You seemed so strong
at the fight the other day

18:50.629 --> 18:53.673
but now your hands
seem so gentle.

18:55.509 --> 18:56.968
Come to think of it,

18:57.719 --> 18:59.887
you are really good
with the barbecue.

19:02.015 --> 19:04.058
Did you learn this
from Mr. MA?

19:08.147 --> 19:11.649
Who's Mr. MA?

19:13.235 --> 19:18.030
A lecherous houseguest.

19:19.074 --> 19:22.952
He taught Bang-ja
some naughty

19:22.995 --> 19:24.787
skills that he used on her.

19:26.915 --> 19:32.211
I scolded him for that.

19:35.340 --> 19:39.385
I see...

19:56.069 --> 19:57.486
Isn't it hot?

19:58.697 --> 20:00.198
I learnt to take the heat
from Mr. MA.

20:00.240 --> 20:03.409
I put you into a mood,
you silly boy.

20:04.411 --> 20:09.415
Oh, no! Are you okay?

20:10.709 --> 20:12.210
Are you okay?

20:12.252 --> 20:14.503
What happened?

20:15.005 --> 20:16.214
Stay still.

20:16.965 --> 20:18.466
You've sprained your ankle.

20:18.508 --> 20:20.384
Stay still.

20:24.223 --> 20:27.475
Oh, dear!
Let her rest her ankle.

20:27.517 --> 20:28.976
Be quiet, you!

20:30.103 --> 20:33.981
Let her rest her foot.

20:34.524 --> 20:35.858
Fortunately,
It's not so swollen.

20:40.322 --> 20:42.406
Is there a stone
to put it up on?

20:42.449 --> 20:46.702
- Oh, Mistress...!
- Bang-ja, come on!

21:19.111 --> 21:20.152
One moment

21:43.719 --> 21:46.178
Your master is weird.

21:46.805 --> 21:49.056
He wants me to be
carried by a servant.

21:50.809 --> 21:51.892
I know.

21:53.937 --> 21:56.647
My clothes are damp
from your wet clothes.

22:00.193 --> 22:01.944
You can walk if you want.

22:03.697 --> 22:07.074
Why are you using
such plain language?

22:09.536 --> 22:11.162
You're not a noble.

22:12.331 --> 22:15.249
I show you respect
when my master is there

22:16.001 --> 22:18.169
but I'm older than yo

22:22.632 --> 22:23.966
Am I heavy?

22:24.009 --> 22:26.802
As light as a feather.

22:28.096 --> 22:30.681
You're good at everything.

22:31.808 --> 22:33.059
Like what?

22:34.519 --> 22:40.483
Fighting, swimming
and barbecuing meat.

22:42.277 --> 22:44.153
You never got the chance
to try the meat.

22:44.613 --> 22:48.407
I didn't need to.
I could tell from the smell.

22:51.286 --> 22:53.788
Must have been
a lovelyjourney.

22:58.460 --> 22:59.877
It's snowing.

23:23.443 --> 23:27.279
You run a rice shop?

23:30.200 --> 23:34.078
It's not my main line ofwork.

23:36.790 --> 23:42.336
Times are tough and
this is no exception.

23:43.088 --> 23:45.673
We're just getting by.

23:45.715 --> 23:50.177
Sorry for interrupting but,

23:50.637 --> 23:54.974
if I were the master,
I'd have carried her myself.

23:57.811 --> 24:01.063
That's the manly thing to do

24:01.189 --> 24:06.068
even if you collapse halfway.

24:09.823 --> 24:10.865
Right?

24:12.534 --> 24:16.662
You don't know anything.

24:18.540 --> 24:20.499
It's called
playing hard to get.

24:22.711 --> 24:26.088
She expected me to carry her
but I didn't.

24:26.798 --> 24:32.678
She gets confused
and falls for me hard.

24:33.305 --> 24:35.890
I see.

24:38.810 --> 24:43.355
My skills are at a different level
to your common ones.

24:47.277 --> 24:53.073
Where did you learn
these skills?

24:54.993 --> 24:58.996
From reading the analects
of Confucious and Mencius.

25:02.125 --> 25:04.585
And also my rival
was only you.

25:07.923 --> 25:09.173
Only me?

25:11.134 --> 25:15.804
You're not really a rival
for me, are you?

25:26.900 --> 25:28.067
Mr. MA.

25:29.110 --> 25:30.069
Yeah?

25:32.030 --> 25:36.784
Where did you learn
those skills?

25:36.826 --> 25:39.620
What, of cutting up
an octopus?

25:39.621 --> 25:43.791
No, the skill you taught me
the other day.

25:44.209 --> 25:49.630
From Mr. JANG.

25:51.383 --> 25:52.883
Mr. JANG?

25:54.719 --> 26:00.599
A playboy from Jeolla
who slept with thousand women.

26:01.893 --> 26:03.185
20 thousand?

26:04.396 --> 26:07.898
You think it's a lie?

26:11.111 --> 26:15.447
He must have been
really handsome.

26:17.742 --> 26:20.202
You don't get women
with your looks.

26:22.914 --> 26:26.667
With money, then?

26:28.461 --> 26:29.878
Silly boy.

26:30.797 --> 26:34.800
He knew how to read
women's minds.

26:35.468 --> 26:39.805
He taught me
the skills to do that.

26:42.309 --> 26:43.475
What's wrong with you?

26:46.021 --> 26:49.189
I don't take on anyone
as a disciple.

26:52.402 --> 26:59.241
Is this for Chun-hyang?
You want her?

26:59.909 --> 27:04.872
I want her so badly.

27:06.916 --> 27:10.794
He might be an noble

27:12.714 --> 27:14.173
but it's so unfair.

27:17.510 --> 27:23.974
Don't think I've made you
a proper disciple.

27:24.017 --> 27:25.976
But since the situation
is urgent,

27:27.520 --> 27:30.773
I'll give you a crash course.

27:32.484 --> 27:37.071
First, sit side by side
like this.

27:37.113 --> 27:41.075
This is the basic position.

27:41.117 --> 27:45.287
Those that sit up like this,
they know nothings.

27:45.288 --> 27:50.542
And then you
lie down like this.

27:55.215 --> 27:58.008
You don't make her lie down?

27:59.302 --> 28:03.013
Stop talking and
try to get me to lie down.

28:03.390 --> 28:05.974
Okay.

28:12.107 --> 28:18.987
It's been a long walk here.
Shall we lie down and talk?

28:34.587 --> 28:38.549
See? Not easy to get her
to lie down.

28:40.009 --> 28:41.468
I see.

28:44.097 --> 28:48.809
But even though
I lie down....

28:50.603 --> 28:51.562
Sit down

29:14.210 --> 29:16.378
This feels nice.

29:17.589 --> 29:28.807
And you lie down like and
stop talking. And, then...

29:30.935 --> 29:32.644
Where do I touch?

29:33.688 --> 29:37.399
You don't touch anything.
Put your shoulder here.

29:40.111 --> 29:45.532
You stare
at her shoulder like this.

29:48.578 --> 29:49.661
At her shoulder?

29:51.289 --> 29:56.084
With all your heart.

29:59.297 --> 30:00.798
Like this.

30:06.846 --> 30:10.808
What?

30:13.436 --> 30:15.562
Thought you
were staring at me.

30:18.399 --> 30:19.566
I wasn't staring at you.

30:21.319 --> 30:23.278
You weren't?

30:27.408 --> 30:32.079
And the final trick
is sneezing

30:35.333 --> 30:37.000
Think I'm coming down
with a cold.

30:54.602 --> 30:55.894
You seem happy.

30:56.396 --> 31:00.899
Are we having chicken
for dinner?

31:06.322 --> 31:10.075
Wasn't sure
if I should tell you

31:11.786 --> 31:16.498
but Chun-hyang wrote to Mong.

31:16.499 --> 31:23.964
She did?

31:24.007 --> 31:24.965
Her servant?

31:25.508 --> 31:26.466
Yes...

31:26.509 --> 31:29.469
I took the letter from her.

31:42.025 --> 31:46.278
It's hot so I won't
be dressed properly

31:46.321 --> 31:49.406
but if you don't mind me
in flimsy clothing,

31:50.033 --> 31:51.909
I'd like to invite you
to my humble abode.

31:53.328 --> 31:59.666
It's so hot as I write that
I want to tear off my clothes.

32:00.126 --> 32:02.085
This doesn't seem right.

32:05.423 --> 32:07.549
How could she write
such a letter...

32:08.927 --> 32:13.555
It's called an SGTH letter.

32:14.015 --> 32:16.850
An SGTH letter?

32:16.935 --> 32:19.478
A letter that Slowly
Gets Them Horny.

32:20.939 --> 32:24.566
Someone else is behind this.

32:28.821 --> 32:31.657
SGTH letters are perfect
for cold bastards.

32:32.700 --> 32:34.826
Once he reads it
he'll come running.

32:35.703 --> 32:38.830
Then you can drive him crazy.

32:40.875 --> 32:44.836
And me?
Should I sleep with Bang-ja?

32:46.589 --> 32:49.091
That's up to you.

32:51.219 --> 32:52.177
I see.

32:54.138 --> 32:58.475
Best not to sleep with him.

33:00.061 --> 33:04.481
