Is it good?

1:13:17.101 --> 1:13:18.768
Love it!

1:13:19.019 --> 1:13:19.977
Good?

1:13:33.450 --> 1:13:39.247
I'm better than Chun-hyang,
aren't I?

1:13:40.082 --> 1:13:44.585
She's nothing.
I'm way hotter than her.

1:14:01.645 --> 1:14:08.276
I've never slept
with a servant before.

1:14:09.319 --> 1:14:11.487
I had many chances

1:14:13.073 --> 1:14:15.074
but didn't want
to take advantage of my position.

1:14:15.075 --> 1:14:17.243
He was into me first.

1:14:19.788 --> 1:14:20.872
What are you saying?

1:14:22.791 --> 1:14:24.250
I mean Bang-ja.

1:14:25.627 --> 1:14:28.171
He liked me first.

1:14:30.632 --> 1:14:35.344
He saw me
and started talking to me.

1:14:37.014 --> 1:14:38.890
He asked me,
'Do you work here?'

1:14:59.620 --> 1:15:02.163
Why is he so important?
He's only a servant.

1:15:02.915 --> 1:15:05.249
He's not important.

1:15:06.710 --> 1:15:09.378
I'm just saying
he liked me first.

1:15:12.633 --> 1:15:15.176
If I hadn't been
a servant...

1:15:27.606 --> 1:15:30.608
You look terrible.

1:15:32.402 --> 1:15:34.278
Take a look in the mirror.

1:15:39.409 --> 1:15:43.287
Find anyone suitable?

1:15:44.540 --> 1:15:49.710
I went round
the whole town but...

1:15:51.171 --> 1:15:54.423
You'll meet someone
very unusual soon.

1:15:55.884 --> 1:15:59.971
Is Chun-hyang
really that special?

1:16:02.182 --> 1:16:08.896
She plays hard to get.

1:16:10.649 --> 1:16:19.073
You'll have to scold her
and imprison her.

1:16:19.408 --> 1:16:22.285
And she'll only obey
after you draw blood.

1:16:25.998 --> 1:16:31.460
Sounds just perfect.

1:16:33.463 --> 1:16:36.465
You've come
to the right place.

1:16:40.721 --> 1:16:42.179
Thank you.

1:16:42.472 --> 1:16:44.807
That's too much.

1:16:44.808 --> 1:16:45.683
See you soon.

1:17:15.922 --> 1:17:20.092
Is that you? Master?

1:17:21.637 --> 1:17:23.554
Your clothes...

1:17:24.723 --> 1:17:29.810
Let me greet you properly.
How have you been?

1:17:30.270 --> 1:17:35.274
Congratulations
on passing the exam.

1:17:36.818 --> 1:17:40.071
Thanks.

1:17:41.281 --> 1:17:44.450
Almost didn't recognize you.

1:17:48.413 --> 1:17:51.874
It's been a long time.

1:17:56.421 --> 1:18:00.716
This place is doing
better than before.

1:18:08.892 --> 1:18:11.769
Take your time. I can wait.

1:18:12.479 --> 1:18:13.562
Master.

1:18:18.902 --> 1:18:26.450
Chun-hyang is unwell

1:18:28.036 --> 1:18:29.787
so she can't see you today.

1:18:41.591 --> 1:18:43.551
She may be ill

1:18:44.094 --> 1:18:46.554
but I'm here after
all these years have passed

1:18:52.018 --> 1:18:52.977
Tell her I'm here.

1:18:54.020 --> 1:19:08.367
But you did leave her so

1:19:10.287 --> 1:19:12.788
it might be better for you
not to see her.

1:19:17.294 --> 1:19:22.089
You've grown insolent.

1:19:23.508 --> 1:19:25.634
Giving me orders?

1:19:31.516 --> 1:19:32.558
What are you doing?

1:19:33.310 --> 1:19:35.394
What could I do?

1:19:36.855 --> 1:19:42.401
I hope you'll take
my position into account.

1:19:46.406 --> 1:19:49.158
Alright.

1:19:51.286 --> 1:19:55.080
Just tell her at least.

1:19:56.917 --> 1:19:58.876
I'll go if she won't see me.

1:20:29.825 --> 1:20:30.908
You didn't take long.

1:20:32.577 --> 1:20:33.577
What did he say?

1:20:34.704 --> 1:20:35.996
Not much.

1:20:36.039 --> 1:20:36.997
Huh?

1:20:39.042 --> 1:20:43.671
Not much.
He wants to see me again.

1:20:47.050 --> 1:20:48.300
Are you going to help them?

1:20:50.011 --> 1:20:50.970
Yes.

1:20:55.308 --> 1:20:56.267
Get to work

1:21:14.202 --> 1:21:15.286
What's Chun-hyang doing?

1:21:15.620 --> 1:21:17.746
Staring into space.

1:21:17.789 --> 1:21:19.081
She's not getting ready?

1:21:19.124 --> 1:21:20.082
No.

1:21:22.043 --> 1:21:23.878
What is she doing?
I told her to get ready.

1:21:32.220 --> 1:21:34.179
She's been caught.

1:21:40.020 --> 1:21:43.564
A round of applause!

1:21:45.233 --> 1:21:46.984
Do this until you're naked!

1:21:47.027 --> 1:21:48.986
Take it off.

1:21:49.613 --> 1:21:51.572
Let's do it again!

1:21:56.036 --> 1:21:57.244
Why aren't you joining us?

1:21:57.287 --> 1:22:01.248
Don't mind me.

1:22:01.291 --> 1:22:04.084
You must feel awkward here

1:22:04.419 --> 1:22:06.837
being from
such a humble background.

1:22:07.923 --> 1:22:10.257
I guess so.

1:22:10.592 --> 1:22:15.763
I understand but I'm worried

1:22:17.515 --> 1:22:22.102
You'll make things
tough for us.

1:22:22.145 --> 1:22:26.565
Don't worry about that.

1:22:27.150 --> 1:22:30.653
You're shutting yourself
offfrom us clerks.

1:22:32.030 --> 1:22:34.281
I'm worried
you're too eager

1:22:34.282 --> 1:22:35.991
to do yourjob.
That won't do.

1:22:37.494 --> 1:22:39.286
- If you don't
-Right.

1:22:39.287 --> 1:22:44.583
know what you're doing
and you're too eager...

1:22:44.584 --> 1:22:51.382
I'll discuss everything with you.

1:22:52.425 --> 1:22:56.095
- Wait!
- Hey!

1:22:56.137 --> 1:23:00.683
I'm glad we have
an understanding.

1:23:00.725 --> 1:23:06.271
I feel I can discuss
what's on my mind.

1:23:10.193 --> 1:23:11.360
This way.

1:23:21.121 --> 1:23:23.288
This is Bang-ja
from Chungpung.

1:23:23.331 --> 1:23:24.748
He's useful to know.

1:23:24.791 --> 1:23:25.749
I see.

1:23:26.626 --> 1:23:27.751
Nice to meet you, Sir.

1:23:27.794 --> 1:23:28.752
Really?

1:23:33.883 --> 1:23:41.557
I heard the owner's daughter,
Chun-hyang,

1:23:42.684 --> 1:23:48.856
that she is a good singer.
I wish to hear her sing.

1:23:49.399 --> 1:23:50.357
Is that possible?

1:23:52.027 --> 1:23:58.115
I told her to get ready
but she's not well.

1:23:58.116 --> 1:24:00.117
There are so many
other girls here.

1:24:00.118 --> 1:24:01.201
Alright, you may go now.

1:24:01.244 --> 1:24:07.875
Don't get involved.

1:24:07.917 --> 1:24:11.462
I really want to hear
her sing.

1:24:13.882 --> 1:24:15.466
Just have a drink.

1:24:20.805 --> 1:24:23.182
This is
what I meant earlier.

1:24:23.892 --> 1:24:25.768
Do you follow me?

1:24:34.319 --> 1:24:36.195
I want to see her,
so bring her.

1:24:36.237 --> 1:24:38.489
What's the problem?

1:24:40.533 --> 1:24:43.660
I'll bring her.
Please don't be angry.

1:24:47.207 --> 1:24:52.086
This is a delicate matter.
Don't get involved.

1:25:01.513 --> 1:25:08.852
I don't look my best but
here I am at your service.

1:25:09.521 --> 1:25:10.771
Good to see you.

1:25:12.607 --> 1:25:14.775
You're beautiful,
just as I heard.

1:25:15.735 --> 1:25:17.194
Not at all, Sir.

1:25:17.779 --> 1:25:20.948
You don't want
to sing for me?

1:25:21.491 --> 1:25:27.371
I'd love to but I'm in
no condition to sing.

1:25:27.872 --> 1:25:30.457
What?

1:25:30.500 --> 1:25:32.960
It's the magistrate's order.

1:25:33.002 --> 1:25:34.753
It's alright.

1:25:34.796 --> 1:25:36.588
She has a problem today.

1:25:36.631 --> 1:25:37.589
Okay.

1:25:38.216 --> 1:25:42.302
Sit beside me and
pour me drinks.

1:25:44.514 --> 1:25:46.473
She's not someone
who does that kind of...

1:25:49.018 --> 1:25:51.353
There must have been
a misunderstanding.

1:25:52.230 --> 1:25:53.856
I'm not a giseng.

1:25:55.400 --> 1:25:56.775
Not a giseng?

1:25:56.776 --> 1:25:58.485
Aren't you
a giseng's daughter?

1:26:00.238 --> 1:26:02.489
If you're going to be rude,

1:26:03.324 --> 1:26:05.033
why don't you
have fun with a giseng?

1:26:06.786 --> 1:26:09.788
How arrogant!

1:26:19.090 --> 1:26:23.677
She's young and doesn't
know any better.

1:26:25.972 --> 1:26:28.473
Please don't be angry.

1:26:28.516 --> 1:26:32.477
This town is a mess.

1:26:32.520 --> 1:26:37.065
Hold him.

1:26:38.318 --> 1:26:39.484
Sir,

1:26:42.238 --> 1:26:43.697
oh, sir!

1:26:54.334 --> 1:26:58.754
I'm not unreasonable.

1:26:59.881 --> 1:27:02.466
I wanted you
to pour me drinks.

1:27:03.968 --> 1:27:05.302
Why are you being
so arrogant?

1:27:07.222 --> 1:27:12.142
Ugly as well as stupid!

1:27:14.312 --> 1:27:18.774
Lock her up
until she sees reason.

1:27:18.816 --> 1:27:19.858
As for him...

1:27:23.988 --> 1:27:26.782
Is he dead?

1:27:33.498 --> 1:27:35.123
I'm drunk, I'm going.

1:27:52.892 --> 1:27:55.394
She has a weak constitution.

1:27:57.730 --> 1:28:01.400
She won't last long in jail.

1:28:02.026 --> 1:28:03.318
Spare her.

1:28:07.323 --> 1:28:11.368
Discuss it
with the clerk, not me.

1:28:13.329 --> 1:28:16.164
But who's in control
ofthis place?

1:28:18.167 --> 1:28:20.168
It's you, sir!

1:28:21.337 --> 1:28:23.797
It's true but...

1:28:27.176 --> 1:28:32.806
he's shut down Chungpung and
levied a lot oftaxes.

1:28:34.100 --> 1:28:38.395
It's out of my control.

1:28:58.833 --> 1:29:02.586
What happened to your face?

1:29:04.213 --> 1:29:06.590
I have something to say...

1:29:10.094 --> 1:29:11.053
Come in.

1:29:14.891 --> 1:29:15.849
Go.

1:29:16.684 --> 1:29:18.769
Would you like something
sweet to drink?

1:29:19.437 --> 1:29:20.562
Go now!

1:29:20.980 --> 1:29:22.773
Let me just clean this bit.

1:29:22.815 --> 1:29:24.858
I said get out!

1:29:28.696 --> 1:29:32.783
Temper, temper!

1:29:39.207 --> 1:29:41.416
Look at you...

1:29:52.178 --> 1:29:53.887
Help me, master.

1:29:55.264 --> 1:29:56.681
I know you can.

1:30:04.023 --> 1:30:05.774
You weren't happy
when I came back,

1:30:08.194 --> 1:30:10.404
asking me
not to get involved.

1:30:12.532 --> 1:30:14.783
Why ask for help now?

1:30:22.166 --> 1:30:27.879
I didn't know any better.

1:30:31.175 --> 1:30:32.884
Forgive me, master.

1:30:40.810 --> 1:30:43.061
I'll sort out everything.

1:30:45.523 --> 1:30:47.065
How can you?

1:30:52.280 --> 1:30:54.239
Don't you trust me?

1:30:57.618 --> 1:30:59.327
You don't have any power.

1:31:01.372 --> 1:31:04.249
I know you'll just ask
for other people's help.

1:31:06.377 --> 1:31:07.961
What else can I do?

1:31:13.301 --> 1:31:19.264
A worm can only crawl.

1:31:24.270 --> 1:31:28.565
So, if you

1:31:33.905 --> 1:31:43.371
have to serve him...

1:31:45.625 --> 1:31:47.250
Ifthere is no other way,

1:31:48.711 --> 1:31:50.170
just do it.

1:31:52.548 --> 1:31:53.590
Really?

1:31:57.094 --> 1:31:58.053
Yes.

1:32:23.037 --> 1:32:26.164
What a picture!

1:32:28.543 --> 1:32:30.001
You'll get her pregnant
in jail.

1:33:09.375 --> 1:33:11.167
What if he doesn't come?

1:33:12.003 --> 1:33:13.253
He will.

1:33:14.088 --> 1:33:15.964
He left his royal badge
with me.

1:33:19.385 --> 1:33:22.679
How about Chun-hyang?

1:33:23.222 --> 1:33:27.601
He said he brought her
but I don't see her.

1:33:27.643 --> 1:33:31.104
This is making me mad.

1:33:31.105 --> 1:33:36.610
You think Mong deceived you?

1:33:37.903 --> 1:33:42.782
He's coming.
I'm sure of it.

1:33:43.117 --> 1:33:45.702
You can't trust nobles!

1:33:55.504 --> 1:34:02.093
Many books teach you
how a ruler should behave

1:34:02.637 --> 1:34:06.890
but it's hard to find
a good magistrate.

1:34:06.932 --> 1:34:14.272
But one such magistrate
has come to our town.

1:34:14.815 --> 1:34:16.524
He's going to say a few words...

1:34:18.903 --> 1:34:21.988
but... he is at present...

1:34:34.418 --> 1:34:42.008
You must have got
bored waiting.

1:34:45.805 --> 1:34:49.182
Some food?

1:34:54.730 --> 1:34:57.565
Aren't you
ashamed of yourself?

1:34:58.818 --> 1:35:07.575
I love it when you get
argumentative.

1:35:11.122 --> 1:35:12.997
You love it, right?

1:35:14.041 --> 1:35:21.548
I'm sure you have naughty
thoughts all the time.

1:35:21.799 --> 1:35:24.467
You into S & M?

1:35:24.802 --> 1:35:26.344
What do you
think you're doing?

1:35:28.097 --> 1:35:32.475
It's alright.
I know about you.

1:35:33.310 --> 1:35:37.647
Stupid is, stupid does.

1:35:39.108 --> 1:35:47.907
Does it feel good?
And this?

1:35:54.373 --> 1:35:57.542
Are you alright?

1:35:59.003 --> 1:36:00.462
Move your hand!

1:36:06.594 --> 1:36:11.639
I love it
when you get angry!

1:36:16.020 --> 1:36:21.483
Sorry, I have to touch you!

1:36:32.411 --> 1:36:34.788
You like it, huh?

1:36:44.215 --> 1:36:45.465
Sir!

1:36:46.675 --> 1:36:50.094
What? You startled me.

1:36:53.015 --> 1:36:54.182
I have something to say.

1:36:54.225 --> 1:36:55.558
What's going on?

1:36:56.018 --> 1:36:57.352
Sir!

1:36:59.897 --> 1:37:03.149
Please forgive Chun-hyang!

1:37:03.192 --> 1:37:05.902
It's that guy
from the other day.

1:37:08.405 --> 1:37:11.449
Please release her.
I know she's done wrong.

1:37:12.409 --> 1:37:14.577
What's wrong with you?

1:37:14.578 --> 1:37:16.079
Please let her go.

1:37:16.121 --> 1:37:22.085
What's going on?
You'll pay for this.

1:37:25.840 --> 1:37:28.675
Let go!

1:37:30.386 --> 1:37:33.972
Please, sir...

1:37:34.014 --> 1:37:35.056
Sir.

1:37:35.099 --> 1:37:37.892
What are you looking at?
Beat him!

1:38:03.752 --> 1:38:22.979
Here comes
the Royal inspector!

1:38:31.530 --> 1:38:36.200
The drink in the gold cup
is the blood ofthe people,

1:38:38.203 --> 1:38:43.249
the food on the pearl plate
is the flesh ofthe people.

1:38:45.920 --> 1:38:49.380
Not sure what it means
but it sounds good.

1:38:49.423 --> 1:38:52.675
It means that the drink comes

1:38:52.676 --> 1:38:56.679
from the efforts
of a thousand people and...

1:38:56.680 --> 1:38:58.014
That's not really the case...

1:38:58.015 --> 1:38:59.098
Okay.

1:38:59.141 --> 1:39:03.561
The new magistrate
welcomed him with a smile.

1:39:05.940 --> 1:39:07.273
He did?

1:39:08.692 --> 1:39:11.819
He wouldn't be intimidated

1:39:12.780 --> 1:39:19.827
But then, the inspector
imprisoned him.

1:39:22.289 --> 1:39:24.582
The joke's gone too far.

1:39:24.583 --> 1:39:28.378
Then, he harasses Chun-hyang.

1:39:29.505 --> 1:39:31.381
I'll ask you one more time.

1:39:32.424 --> 1:39:34.300
He was a corrupt magistrate

1:39:34.301 --> 1:39:36.302
but still
an order of an official,

1:39:36.303 --> 1:39:38.596
why did you
refuse to serve him?

1:39:38.889 --> 1:39:43.309
I told you.
I'm not a giseng.

1:39:44.311 --> 1:39:47.188
Why should I serve him?

1:39:55.781 --> 1:39:57.657
Not a giseng?

1:40:01.412 --> 1:40:05.873
Think your behaviour is
better than that of a giseng?

1:40:05.874 --> 1:40:10.211
What do you know about me?

1:40:12.047 --> 1:40:14.215
I know nothing
of your behaviour

1:40:14.800 --> 1:40:18.344
but who knows
you're nothing but talk

1:40:19.513 --> 1:40:22.181
You'll tell the truth once
you're beaten.

1:40:27.771 --> 1:40:28.855
Spit it out.

1:40:30.899 --> 1:40:36.654
Chastity means nothing
in this filthy world.

1:40:43.037 --> 1:40:45.663
If you refused while not keeping
your chastity in private,

1:40:47.332 --> 1:40:49.125
I'll beat you to death.

1:41:03.515 --> 1:41:05.099
What's this?

1:41:09.688 --> 1:41:14.859
She has a husband.

1:41:16.236 --> 1:41:20.114
Please release her.

1:41:21.158 --> 1:41:25.453
Is that so?
Release her, then.

1:41:25.496 --> 1:41:26.454
Yes, Sir.

1:41:36.131 --> 1:41:45.681
Is this lowly man
your husband?

1:41:51.980 --> 1:41:57.944
No, he's just a servant
at my house.

1:42:26.723 --> 1:42:30.351
Royal Inspector!

1:42:32.604 --> 1:42:34.856
You're right.

1:42:36.400 --> 1:42:41.571
I haven't kept my chastity
so I should have served him.

1:42:42.489 --> 1:42:43.489
When...

1:42:51.331 --> 1:42:53.040
my love left,

1:42:53.792 --> 1:42:58.796
he asked me
to keep a promise.

1:43:00.799 --> 1:43:05.469
I was torn.

1:43:07.389 --> 1:43:13.060
Break the promise
to my love

1:43:13.896 --> 1:43:19.483
or be beaten to death
by a nobleman.

1:43:31.705 --> 1:43:37.835
Please pass my regards
to Mong ofthe YI family.

1:43:47.888 --> 1:43:51.849
Chun-hyang, open your eyes.

1:43:59.524 --> 1:44:04.695
It's me, I'm back.

1:44:05.447 --> 1:44:09.992
You were waiting for me.

1:44:10.494 --> 1:44:12.662
Open your eyes.

1:44:17.876 --> 1:44:26.759
I only wanted to test you.

1:44:33.016 --> 1:44:37.144
If you die,

1:44:39.022 --> 1:44:42.400
what's the point of me
having become a royal inspector?

1:45:09.803 --> 1:45:11.053
Hold on.

1:45:11.430 --> 1:45:15.891
The Royals' have gone crazy
about her story offidelity

1:45:16.685 --> 1:45:21.480
They're going to erect
a monument in her honor.

1:45:24.192 --> 1:45:25.401
Great.

1:45:26.528 --> 1:45:30.239
Things have gotten
more than great for Mong

1:45:30.991 --> 1:45:34.160
He's been promoted
by two grades, too.

1:45:37.539 --> 1:45:44.420
She betrayed you
so she won't come, will she?

1:45:44.421 --> 1:45:45.796
Of course not.

1:45:47.549 --> 1:45:52.470
If she does...
You never know.

1:45:53.096 --> 1:45:57.058
If she comes,
don't beg her to stay.

1:45:59.269 --> 1:46:00.227
What do you mean?

1:46:00.979 --> 1:46:05.066
The game's up
if you beg her to stay.

1:46:06.526 --> 1:46:09.236
Act cold.

1:46:09.905 --> 1:46:14.575
Act as if you're
happy she's leaving you.

1:46:18.121 --> 1:46:19.705
Don't worry.

1:46:20.624 --> 1:46:22.500
I was going to do that anyway.

1:46:33.261 --> 1:46:38.891
Comb your hair.

1:46:39.267 --> 1:46:42.269
A man's style
is all about his hair.

1:47:21.017 --> 1:47:23.978
They're releasing you today.
Hold on a bit more.

1:47:24.813 --> 1:47:25.771
Yes,

1:47:29.943 --> 1:47:31.569
I heard.

1:47:31.611 --> 1:47:32.862
You're angry at me?

1:47:34.781 --> 1:47:36.574
What's there
to be angry about?

1:47:39.619 --> 1:47:40.578
Why did you do it?

1:47:43.915 --> 1:47:45.166
Why?

1:47:46.793 --> 1:47:50.087
I told you everything
about our plan.

1:47:50.088 --> 1:47:51.338
Why did you do it?

1:47:52.382 --> 1:47:55.259
When I met the magistrate,

1:47:56.219 --> 1:47:58.679
an idea came to me.

1:48:01.558 --> 1:48:05.352
Shall we make up
a fake story?

1:48:06.688 --> 1:48:11.775
It'll help us both.

1:48:18.366 --> 1:48:21.869
This was all set up.

1:48:22.913 --> 1:48:29.793
You knew that,
so why did you do it?

1:48:30.295 --> 1:48:31.587
I wanted to help you.

1:48:33.006 --> 1:48:38.260
The plan had to be
convincing, right?

1:48:41.806 --> 1:48:46.352
I've not done anything for you

1:48:51.024 --> 1:48:52.691
and I always felt
bad about that.

1:48:55.028 --> 1:49:00.157
Plus, I couldn't trust Mong.

1:49:07.123 --> 1:49:08.290
Wait!

1:49:16.299 --> 1:49:21.887
I have to tell you something.

1:49:23.890 --> 1:49:25.057
What?

1:49:26.101 --> 1:49:27.059
I...

1:49:31.398 --> 1:49:32.898
love you.

1:49:38.321 --> 1:49:39.780
What did you say?

1:49:40.490 --> 1:49:41.907
I love you.

1:49:44.202 --> 1:49:49.331
I'm a servant so
I don't have the right.

1:49:52.711 --> 1:49:53.877
But, I love you.

1:50:07.726 --> 1:50:10.603
Lucky Chun-hyang!

1:50:15.400 --> 1:50:17.234
Aren't you dizzy?

1:50:21.197 --> 1:50:22.948
I have to take
Bang-ja with me.

1:50:30.373 --> 1:50:31.373
What?

1:50:31.374 --> 1:50:33.542
I'm not going anywhere
without him.

1:50:40.383 --> 1:50:41.800
Have you gone mad?

1:50:43.386 --> 1:50:45.179
If I can't,
I'll tell them everything.

1:50:57.734 --> 1:51:01.153
Weird people.

1:51:03.490 --> 1:51:08.994
Truly weird.

1:51:09.412 --> 1:51:15.084
I know. But the three of us
got along surprisingly well.

1:51:16.127 --> 1:51:19.296
I was the one in pain.

1:51:22.008 --> 1:51:24.677
No, I thought
I was the one in pain.

1:51:34.896 --> 1:51:35.979
Bang-ja!

1:52:06.720 --> 1:52:07.803
What?

1:52:08.471 --> 1:52:10.180
There's a strange fish.

1:52:11.224 --> 1:52:12.558
Fish?

1:52:26.114 --> 1:52:28.073
Where the hell is it?

1:53:06.488 --> 1:53:09.531
Dear me, I pushed her.

1:53:47.195 --> 1:53:51.365
He kept sending people
after us.

1:53:53.827 --> 1:53:57.287
We kept running.

1:53:59.207 --> 1:54:00.666
I'm not surprised.

1:54:02.210 --> 1:54:04.086
He's one hell of a man.

1:54:04.838 --> 1:54:07.381
But you are amazing.

1:54:08.424 --> 1:54:11.969
You ran offwith
an aristocrat's woman.

1:54:16.474 --> 1:54:18.350
She wasn't his,

1:54:20.395 --> 1:54:22.062
but mine.

1:54:49.591 --> 1:54:51.633
This is she?

1:54:53.595 --> 1:54:55.387
She survived but

1:55:02.228 --> 1:55:07.399
became like a child.

1:55:08.776 --> 1:55:12.279
You've been on the run
with her like this?

1:55:14.782 --> 1:55:15.908
Yes.

1:55:17.994 --> 1:55:19.745
A heartbreaking tale.

1:55:21.664 --> 1:55:23.999
I'll write a good story
for you.

1:55:24.584 --> 1:55:27.461
The love of a servant.

1:55:27.795 --> 1:55:31.381
No, not like that.

1:55:33.134 --> 1:55:34.176
Then what?

1:55:35.136 --> 1:55:37.262
Beautify the story.

1:55:42.435 --> 1:55:49.691
Chun-hyang was on a swing
on a beautiful May day.

1:55:51.861 --> 1:55:57.282
She fell in love
with Mong at first sight.

1:55:58.868 --> 1:56:03.747
He went to Seoul,

1:56:03.790 --> 1:56:05.749
passed the exam,
she waited for him

1:56:09.587 --> 1:56:17.177
and they lived
happily ever after.

1:56:19.222 --> 1:56:24.726
If you want, I'll write it
like that but why?

1:56:25.853 --> 1:56:27.562
Because it's something

1:56:32.193 --> 1:56:33.986
she never got to have.

1:56:37.198 --> 1:56:39.366
The title should be

1:56:46.332 --> 1:56:54.506
'The Tale of Chun-hyang'

1:57:08.896 --> 1:57:13.859
'The Tale of Chun-hyang'.
A great title.

1:57:18.031 --> 1:57:22.576
And put in this scene.

1:57:35.673 --> 1:57:41.678
It's when the master
is really in love with her.

1:57:42.889 --> 1:57:48.393
He sings a song for her.

1:57:49.604 --> 1:57:55.859
Come here and I'll carry
you on my back.

1:57:59.822 --> 1:58:03.366
Come here

1:58:08.790 --> 1:58:12.084
I'm no good at singing, so...

1:58:15.588 --> 1:58:19.382
But you're
the hero ofthe tale.

1:58:20.134 --> 1:58:25.097
I don't care what kind of
role I play in the tale.

1:58:28.434 --> 1:58:30.602
I'm the hero in my heart.

1:58:35.316 --> 1:58:38.193
I'll try again properly.

1:58:40.988 --> 1:58:52.040
Come here and I'll carry you.

1:58:52.416 --> 1:59:10.350
You're my love,
my true love...
